# Copy to `terraform.tfvars` in this directory (gitignored) for local non-secret values.
# Do not commit `terraform.tfvars` or `*.auto.tfvars` with real data.
#
# API credentials — never put them in tfvars. Export in your shell or CI instead:
#   export HCLOUD_TOKEN="..."
#   export CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN="..."
#
# After you declare `variable` blocks in *.tf, add assignments here, for example:
#   location     = "nbg1"
#   server_type  = "cx22"
#
# For extra sensitive Terraform variables you define yourself, prefer TF_VAR_name in CI
# or a gitignored tfvars file — same rule: do not commit real values.
